#: views/admin-settings-view.php:757
msgid "Matching & Re-ranking Mechanism"
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:758
msgid "Step 1: Database Pre-filtering"
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:759
msgid ""
"Plugin queries the database to find candidate matching posts. Candidates are "
"pre-filtered by post type, taxonomies (categories/tags), and WPML/Polylang "
"languages first to prevent slow database queries."
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:761
msgid "Step 2: Cosine Similarity"
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:762
msgid ""
"PHP calculates mathematical cosine similarity between the current post's "
"text embedding vector and all candidates vectors. The top matches (e.g. 50 "
"items) are kept."
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:764
msgid "Step 3: LLM Re-ranking"
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:765
msgid ""
"The top similar candidates are sent to the selected OpenRouter Chat LLM "
"along with instructions. The LLM evaluates context relevance and ranks the "
"best results."
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:769
msgid "API Quotas & Mutex Caching"
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:770
msgid "Daily Limits & Costs Control"
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:771
msgid ""
"To prevent surprise bills, separate daily limits block API operations once "
"exceeded, automatically falling back to native category recommendation "
"matching. Quotas reset at midnight based on local WordPress timezone "
"settings."
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:773
msgid "Mutex Lock (Cache Stampede Protection)"
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:774
msgid ""
"During cache expiration, if multiple concurrent requests hit the same post, "
"only the first request makes an external API call to OpenRouter. Subsequent "
"concurrent requests immediately receive a native category fallback list "
"rather than blocking execution or making duplicate costly API calls. Lock "
"expires after 60 seconds."
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:778
msgid "WooCommerce Support & Filters"
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:779
msgid "Dynamic WooCommerce Pages"
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:780
msgid ""
"When rendering recommendations on WooCommerce Cart, Checkout, or Order "
"Received (Thank You) pages, the plugin automatically overrides generic page "
"titles/descriptions with products from the active customer's cart or order "
"details."
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:782
msgid "Cache Isolation & Security"
msgstr ""

#: views/admin-settings-view.php:783
msgid ""
"Recommendation caching keys are partitioned using secure MD5 cart item "
"hashes and order IDs. This prevents different users from seeing each other's "
"cached product recommendations on WooCommerce pages."
msgstr ""

